   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Sabinus to Eutyches, greetings. I want you to know that today, which is the 28th, 'Heron the Little' was appointed by the epistrategos to bear the expense of the gymnasiarchy for a period of two months, viz., since he is fourth, for Phamenoth and Pharmouthi of the approaching year 2[.] [- - -]</ab>
